{"questionId":"12207","questionHtml":"<p class=\"indent1\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;\">Hence find the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\left( {1 - \\gamma } \\right)^6}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>γ</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>6</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\left( {1 - \\gamma } \\right)^6} = {\\left( { - {\\gamma ^2}} \\right)^6}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>γ</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>6</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>γ</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>6</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = {\\left( \\gamma&nbsp; \\right)^{12}}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mi>γ</mi>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>12</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = {\\left( {{\\gamma ^3}} \\right)^4}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>γ</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = {\\left( { - 1} \\right)^4}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = 1\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD&nbsp;2</strong></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\left( {1 - \\gamma } \\right)^6}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mi>γ</mi>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mn>6</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = 1 - 6\\gamma&nbsp; + 15{\\gamma ^2} - 20{\\gamma ^3} + 15{\\gamma ^4} - 6{\\gamma ^5} + {\\gamma ^6}\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mi>γ</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>15</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>20</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>15</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>5</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>6</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>M1</strong></em> for attempt at binomial expansion.</p>\n<p>use of any previous result e.g.&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" = 1 - 6\\gamma&nbsp; + 15{\\gamma ^2} + 20 - 15\\gamma&nbsp; + 6{\\gamma ^2} + 1\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mi>γ</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>15</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>20</mn>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>15</mn>\n  <mi>γ</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>6</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>γ</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"&nbsp;= 1\">\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong>Note: </strong>As the question uses the word ‘hence’, other methods that&nbsp;do not use previous results are awarded no marks.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12207","referenceCode":"EXM.2.AHL.TZ0.20a.iii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Hence find the value of ( 1 − γ ) 6 .","paper":"2","level":"HL","questionNumber":"a.iii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.12—Complex numbers introduction","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.14—Introduction to matrices"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}